OL,3,COver 10 percent of deaths in Wales due
OL,4,Cto smoking
OL,6,FMore than one in ten deaths of those
OL,7,Faged over 35 in Wales is due to
OL,8,Fsmoking.
OL,10,FNew analysis from Public Health Wales
OL,11,Fhas shown that more than 3,800 deaths
OL,12,Fin Wales in 2022 were because of
OL,13,Fsmoking.
OL,15,FLatest figures have also shown than on
OL,16,Faverage more than 17,000 hospital
OL,17,Fadmissions each year were down to
OL,18,Fsmoking.
