OL,3,COver 10 percent of deaths in Wales due
OL,4,Cto smoking
OL,6,FThe study, Smoking attributable
OL,7,Fmortality and hospital admissions for
OL,8,FWales 2020-22, seeks to also highlight
OL,9,Fthe inequalities between the most and
OL,10,Fleast deprived communities.
OL,12,FIt found that the rate of deaths
OL,13,Fattributable to smoking was three
OL,14,Ftimes higher in the most deprived
OL,15,Fcommunities compared to the least.
OL,17,FHospital admissions were also twice as
OL,18,Fhigh for residents of the most
OL,19,Fdeprived communities compared to the
OL,20,Fleast.
