OL,3,COver 10 percent of deaths in Wales due
OL,4,Cto smoking
OL,6,FChris Emmerson, Consultant in Public
OL,7,FHealth at Public Health Wales, said:
OL,8,F"These statistics are a stark reminder
OL,9,Fof the devastating impact that smoking
OL,10,Fcontinues to have on the health of the
OL,11,FWelsh population, particularly in our
OL,12,Fmost deprived communities.
OL,14,F"Despite the real progress we have
OL,15,Fmade reducing the numbers taking up
OL,16,Fsmoking and support smokers to quit,
OL,17,Fit's clear that we need to make every
OL,18,Feffort to tackle smoking if we are to
OL,19,Faddress these huge health and
OL,20,Ffinancial costs for the people of
OL,21,FWales."
