OL,6,FPublic Health Wales say they welcomed
OL,7,Fthe announcement in the King's Speech
OL,8,Fin July that the Tobacco and Vapes
OL,9,FBill, first introduced by the previous
OL,10,FUK Conservative Government, will
OL,11,Freturn to parliament in the current
OL,12,Fterm under Labour.
OL,14,FProvisions of the previous Bill
OL,15,Fincluded banning the sale of tobacco
OL,16,Fto everyone born after 1 January 2009.
OL,18,F"This new analysis highlights the
OL,19,Fbenefits that ambitious policies to
OL,20,Fprevent young people from starting to
OL,21,Fsmoke could deliver" Mr Emmerson added.
